(2006) }} }} "'Crowded'" is a 2006 R&B song released as the first official single from Jeannie Ortega's debut album, [[No Place Like BKLYN]]. The song was also featured on the soundtrack to the film [[Stick It]]. The song also features underground rapper Papoose. The song charted on the Hot 100 and did well on Pop 100 Airplay.
